        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Divide the <strong>cheddar & pesto filling</strong> between the<strong> ciabatta base[s] </strong>and<strong> </strong>spread almost to the edges, leaving a small border</p><p>Top with a<strong> ciabatta lid</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>cheddar & pesto toastie[s]</strong></p>",
