        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the<strong> cheddar & pesto toastie[s] </strong>and cover with a smaller pan</p><p>Add a heavy weight (e.g. several tins) to the top pan and cook for 3-4 min per side, checking occasionally or until the ciabatta is golden and the cheese has melted</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? You may need to do this in batches!</p>",
